title: Imagine:
body: The Avengers’ plan to attack Thanos included you, one of the smartest and strongest avenger and Steve’s fiancé, to get into his ship without his guards following you. But, of course, it was a long risk to take. Although you agreed rightaway, everyone was expecting the Cap to argue when, before he did, Wanda voluntereed herself for the task. And Cap knew the reason; she had always been in love with you, protecting you all the time and being your mentor whenever needed.

He is wicked handsy, all around! I bet he’s the kinda guy who wants your toes tucked under his thighs while you each each on the couch and he wants you to sit on his lap while you watch the sun rise in his backyard. Sweet, unnecessary touches that make your heart flutter.

—
